description: Keep generated asset scripts read-only and edit source scripts only
alwaysApply: true
---

# Script editing boundary

Treat script files in any `assets` directory as generated output.

- Do not edit JavaScript files inside `assets` folders.
- Make script changes only in matching source files inside `_scripts` folders.
- If both locations exist, `_scripts` is the single source of truth and `assets` should only be updated by the build process.
